an, J., Livingston, W.C., Keil, S.L., The sun in a noncycling state (1992) Publ. Astron. Soc. Pac., 104, pp. 1139-1143; Willson, R.C., Total solar irradiance trend during solar cycles 21 and 22 (1997) Science, 277, pp. 1963-1965; Willson, R.C., Hudson, H.S., Solar luminosity variations in solar cycle 21 (1988) Nature, 332, pp. 810-812; Zhang, Q., Soon, W.H., Baliunas, S.L., Lockwood, G.W., Skiff, B.A., Radick, R.R., A method of determining possible brightness variations of the sun in past centuries from observations of solar-type stars (1994) Astrophys. J., 427, pp. L111-L114","Bard, E.; CEREGE, Universite d Aix-Marseille, UMR-CNRS 6635, Europole de l'Arbois, BP 80, 13545 Aixen-Provence Cedex 4, France; email: bard@cerege.fr",,,,,,,,02806509,,,,"English","Tellus, Ser. B Chem. Phys. Meteorol.",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-0033929083
